when the author is young, he draw a picture, just like this, every adult who saw the picture would mistakenly it as a hat. Actually, this is a snake, and a elephant is in its stomach.whenever the author would try to correct this confusion, he was advised to set aside drawing and take up a more practical or mature hobby. Mybe the author had a great career as a painter, but this opportunity was crushed by the misunderstanding of the adults.
Now as an adult, the author become a pilot. One day, his plane was crashed in the desert, far from civilization. Here, the author met a yong boy he refers to as "the little prince". the little prince asks him to draw a sheep, the author shows him his old picture of the elephant inside the snake
